metadata.name: Raven Carries the Moon
metadata.description:
Northwest Coastal form line art of Raven carrying the Moon across a wintery night sky. Includes a one hour virtual astrology reading with The Ascendant Healing & Metaphysics valued at $75 (for anyone 18+)

About the Artist: Ezra (MetzilMazatl/Moon Deer) is a two spirit Quinault & Chichimeca artist who resides on the traditional lands of the Spokane Tribe, raised and hosted by the Yakama Nation in the Pacific North West (PNW). They have studied art and graphic design professionally for over 16 years.
